<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<style>
    @font-face {
        font-family: 'Pretendard-Regular';
        font-weight: 400;
        font-display: swap;
        src: local('Pretendard Regular'), url(https://fonts.tonystreet.com/fonts/pretendard/Pretendard-Regular.woff2) format('woff2'), url(https://fonts.tonystreet.com/fonts/pretendard/Pretendard-Regular.woff) format('woff');
    }

    @font-face {
        font-family: 'CodecCold-Bold';
        font-weight: normal;
        font-style: normal;
        src: local("※"), url("https://fonts.tonystreet.com/fonts/codec-cold/Codec-Cold-Bold.eot?#iefix") format("embedded-opentype"), url("https://fonts.tonystreet.com/fonts/codec-cold/Codec-Cold-Bold.woff") format("woff");
    }

    body {
        margin: 0
    }

    #logo {
        margin: 20px 0 0 20px;
        width: 140px
    }

    #error_page {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        width: 400px;
        text-align: center
    }

    #error_page h1 {
        font-family: "CodecCold-Bold";
        width: 100%;
        color: #FF158A;
        font-size: 48px;
        letter-spacing: 1.44px;
        margin-bottom: 20px
    }

    #error_page p {
        font-family: "Pretendard-Regular";
        font-size: 16px;
        letter-spacing: -0.64px;
        color: #222;
        line-height: 27.4px;
        margin-bottom: 36px
    }

    #error_page a {
        font-family: "Pretendard-Regular";
        display: inline-block;
        width: 165px;
        height: 50px;
        line-height: 51px;
        border: 1px solid #120909;
        background: #fff;
        color: #120909;
        letter-spacing: -0.64px;
        text-decoration: none
    }

    @media screen and (max-device-width: 1024px) {
        #error_page {
            width: 100%
        }

        #error_page h1 {
            font-size: 32px
        }

        #error_page a, #error_page p {
            font-size: 15px;
            letter-spacing: -0.6px;
        }

        #logo {
            margin: 16px 0 0 16px;
            width: 120px
        }

        #error_page a {
            width: 150px;
            height: 48px;
        }
    }
</style>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" name="viewport">
    <title>404</title>
    <link href="/css/error.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"/>
</head>
<body>
<img id="logo" src="https://tonyproduct.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/IMG1705lR470449610.png"/>
<div id="error_page">
    <h1>404 ERROR</h1>
    <p>
        요청하신 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.<br>
        입력하신 주소가 올바른지 다시 확인해 주세요.<br>
        해당 페이지가 변경되었거나 삭제되었을 수 있습니다.
    </p>
    <a href="https://tonymoly.com" id="go_mall">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>